title: Interaction Design: Beyond Human-Computer Interaction, 4th Ed.
description:
Interaction Design: Beyond Human-Computer Interaction, 4th Edition


by Jenny Preece, Helen Sharp, Yvonne Rogers


This torrent contains an EPub that was created directly from Wiley's eText of this book, and includes all the media and interactive bits (i.e. videos, buttons that show hidden text, etc).

There is also a PDF version, which has been converted from the epub using Calibre, but I wouldn't recommend you use it. None of the videos or other interactive things will work on the PDF. I did try to make sure any stuff that was hidden behind buttons got shown, but I can't guarantee that everything in the EPub version will be there in the PDF
